2ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Welcome%20To%20The%20Jungle%20Movie%20Updates%3A%20Akshay%2C%20Suniel%2C%20Paresh%20return%20for%20laughter%20riot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782436314000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132005456%2Cimgsize-89024.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwelcome-to-the-jungle-movie-review-release-live-update-akshay-kumar-suniel-shetty-disha-patani-welcome-to-the-jungle-review-and-box-office-collection%2Fliveblog%2F132005456.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F132005456.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump's%20DOT%20proposes%20new%20rules%20for%20driverless%20vehicles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223987%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20automobile%20brake%20pedal%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3dbcda360acd489560b9d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222740%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20DOT%20is%20pushing%20for%20regulatory%20changes%20to%20enable%20the%20development%20of%20autonomous%20vehicles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENHTSA%20proposes%20allowing%20the%20removal%20of%20brake%20pedals%20and%20steering%20wheels%20for%20AVs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESafety%20advocates%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20clarity%20on%20vehicle%20operations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20riding%20in%20a%20car%20with%20no%20steering%20wheel%20or%20pedals%20is%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20becoming%20reality%2C%20thanks%20to%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Transportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20is%20considering%20a%20regulatory%20change%20that%20could%20help%20accelerate%20the%20rollout%20of%20purpose-built%20robotaxis%2C%20including%20vehicles%20without%20steering%20wheels%20or%20brake%20pedals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20DOT%20proposed%20updating%20federal%20vehicle%20safety%20rules%20to%20no%20longer%20require%20brake%20pedals%20in%20vehicles%20designed%20to%20operate%20exclusively%20with%20automated%20driving%20systems.%20If%20adopted%2C%20the%20change%20would%20remove%20a%20hurdle%20for%20companies%20such%20as%20Tesla%20and%20Zoox%2C%20which%20are%20developing%20autonomous%20vehicles%20without%20traditional%20driver%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20is%20now%20open%20for%20public%20comment%20for%2030%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20is%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20effort%20by%20federal%20regulators%20to%20modernize%20vehicle%20rules%20for%20the%20autonomous%20era.%20The%20National%20Highway%20Traffic%20Safety%20Administration%20has%20previously%20proposed%20eliminating%20requirements%20tied%20to%20features%20such%20as%20windshield%20defoggers%2C%20wipers%2C%20and%20tire%20placards%20for%20certain%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-fully-self-driving-cars-are-almost-impossible-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eself-driving%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20During%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20regulators%20finalized%20a%20rule%20allowing%20autonomous%20vehicles%20to%20operate%20without%20steering%20wheels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20moment%2C%20companies%20that%20want%20to%20deploy%20vehicles%20missing%20federally%20required%20equipment%20must%20obtain%20government%20exemptions%2C%20and%20those%20exemptions%20come%20with%20limits%20on%20how%20many%20vehicles%20can%20be%20put%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20regulations%20would%20allow%20companies%20like%20Zoox%20to%20scale%20quickly.%20At%20present%2C%20Zoox%20is%20waiting%20on%20an%20exemption%20on%20driver-control%20requirements%20so%20it%20can%20produce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-zoox-robotaxi-production-upgraded-design-100-vehicles-week-expansion-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E100%20robotaxis%20a%20week%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENHTSA%20Administrator%20Jonathan%20Morrison%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20latest%20proposal%20is%20an%20effort%20to%20tear%20down%20%26quot%3Bpointless%20barriers%20to%20innovative%20designs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nterior%20view%20of%20a%20Waymo%20self%20driving%20car%20driving%20through%20downtown%20San%20Francisco%2C%20California%20in%20fully%20autonomous%20mode%2C%20June%207%2C%202024.%20(Photo%20by%20Smith%20Collection%2FGado%2FGetty%20Images)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3db5a6e218c3b62535d619%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223262%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20a%20Waymo.%3Cp%3ESmith%20Collection%2FGado%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPhilip%20Koopman%2C%20an%20emeritus%20professor%20of%20electrical%20and%20computer%20engineering%20at%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University%2C%20said%20that%20removing%20%26quot%3Bhistorically%20unintended%20restrictions%20on%20autonomous%20vehicles%26quot%3B%20is%20generally%20a%20good%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20appropriate%20to%20modify%20the%20Federal%20Motor%20Vehicle%20Safety%20Standards%20to%20remove%20unintended%20barriers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-recall-robotaxis-entered-freeway-construction-zones-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edriverless%20vehicle%3C%2Fa%3E%20deployment%20by%20removing%20dependencies%20on%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20human%20driver%2C%20which%20this%20latest%20proposal%20does%2C%26quot%3B%20Koopman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20equally%20important%20point%20is%20that%20while%20NHTSA%20is%20busy%20removing%20unintended%20barriers%2C%20there%20are%20no%20FMVSS%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eparts%20that%20are%20specific%20to%20autonomous%20vehicles%2C%26quot%3B%20Koopman%20added%20of%20the%20regulations.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20long%20past%20time%20to%20see%20movement%20in%20adding%20new%20safety%20standards%20relevant%20to%20this%20new%20technology%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20could%20be%20especially%20significant%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybercab-robotaxi-production-video-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla's%20Cybercab%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Amazon-owned%20Zoox%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20developing%20robotaxis%20without%20conventional%20driver%20controls.%20Multiple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautonomous-vehiecle-industry-humanoid-robots-startups-hiring-talent-pool-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAV%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20voiced%20their%20support%20for%20the%20NHTSA%20proposal%20through%20public%20comment%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWaymo%20and%20Zoox%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20in%20April%20that%20the%20revised%20regulations%20would%20reduce%20their%20compliance%20costs%2C%20while%20Tesla%20wrote%20that%20it%20would%20like%20the%20agency%20to%20consider%20adding%20more%20vehicle%20types%20to%20the%20pedal%20exemption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c576e09d-b10b-4378-b14d-8976b80fa4fd%5C%22%3ESafety%20complexities%20remain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Automobile%20Association%20said%20in%20its%20public%20comment%20to%20NHTSA%20that%20while%20it%20supports%20easing%20regulations%20for%20fully%20autonomous%20vehicles%2C%20transparency%20is%20key%2C%20especially%20for%20passengers%20and%20emergency%20responders%20who%20may%20not%20know%20how%20to%20operate%20a%20vehicle%20without%20such%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20boards%20a%20Zoox%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3dbf8be218c3b62535d64b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222025%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInterior%20of%20a%20Zoox%20robotaxi.%3Cp%3EJay%20Janner%2FThe%20Austin%20American-Statesman%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Advocates%20for%20Highway%20and%20Auto%20Safety%20echoed%20these%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNHTSA%20presents%20no%20research%20or%20analysis%20of%20the%20potential%20safety%20impacts%20of%20removing%20the%20display%20and%20provides%20no%20discussion%20of%20the%20possible%20concerns%20not%20only%20for%20passengers%20but%20also%20potentially%20for%20first%20responders%20who%20may%20need%20to%20know%20the%20potential%20for%20the%20vehicle%20to%20be%20in%20gear%20following%20a%20collision%20or%20other%20system%20failure%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20advocacy%20organization%20wrote%20in%20its%20public%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDan%20O'Dowd%2C%20founder%20of%20The%20Dawn%20Project%2C%20an%20AV%20safety%20advocacy%20group%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20robotaxis%20should%20be%20required%20to%20meet%20certain%20reliability%20standards%20before%20they%20can%20have%20no%20physical%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-robotaxi-unsupervised-service-area-austin-stock-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla's%20'Robotaxis%3C%2Fa%3E'%20are%20nowhere%20near%20the%20reliability%20level%20required%20to%20remove%20the%20brake%20pedal%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Dowd%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20removal%20of%20physical%20controls%20should%20only%20be%20granted%20to%20robotaxi%20companies%20who%20have%20conclusively%20proven%20their%20software%20is%20safe%20for%20autonomous%2C%20unsupervised%20driving.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%2C%20Waymo%2C%20and%20Zoox%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%