20where%20many%20young%20people%20have%20taken%20to%20swimming%20unattended%20in%20lakes%20and%20canals%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2026%2F06%2F25%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fheat-wave.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhotos%20show%20how%20extreme%20heat%20is%20affecting%20businesses%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20daily%20life%20across%20Europe%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20locals%20and%20tourists%20are%20doing%20their%20best%20to%20beat%20the%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20thermometer%20in%20Brussels%20displayed%20a%20temperature%20of%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20or%20113%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227728%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20thermometer%20shows%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20Brussels%2C%20Belgium.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d436ba25092c74cc9f238%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBRUSSELS%2C%20BELGIUM%20-%20JUNE%2023%3A%20A%20thermometer%20shows%2045%C2%B0C%20(113%C2%B0F)%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Berlaymont%2C%20the%20EU%20Commission%20headquarter%20on%20June%2023%2C%202026%20in%20Brussels%2C%20Belgium.%20Various%20European%20governments%20issued%20health%20warnings%20this%20week%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20high%20temperatures%2C%20which%20were%20nearing%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20many%20large%20cities.%3Cp%3EThierry%20Monasse%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDogs%20and%20humans%20alike%20splashed%20in%20sidewalk%20sprinklers%20and%20fountains%20around%20Brussels%20for%20a%20break%20from%20the%20heat.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224618%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dog%20plays%20with%20water%20in%20Brussels.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d49cc360acd489560b43b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223079%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20dog%20plays%20with%20water%20sprays%20during%20a%20heatwave%20in%20Brussels%20on%20June%2025%2C%202026.%20At%20least%20101%20million%20Europeans%20were%20expected%20to%20experience%20temperatures%20of%20over%2035C%20on%20June%2025%2C%202026%2C%20in%20a%20punishing%20and%20increasingly%20deadly%20heatwave%20hotter%20than%20weather%20in%20parts%20of%20Africa.%3Cp%3ENicolas%20TUCAT%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBillboards%20in%20Venice%2C%20Italy%2C%20issued%20heat%20wave%20alerts%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20when%20temperatures%20reached%2095%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225045%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20billboard%20warns%20of%20a%20heat%20wave%20alert%20in%20Venice%2C%20Italy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d49cce218c3b62535d0c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223367%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVENICE%2C%20ITALY%20-%20JUNE%2024%3A%20An%20illuminated%20sign%20warns%20of%20a%20heatwave%20alert%2C%20on%20June%2024%2C%202026%20in%20Venice%2C%20Italy.%20Venice%20is%20hit%20by%20a%20severe%20heatwave%2C%20with%20temperatures%20reaching%2035%C2%B0C%20today%2C%20as%20an%20African%20anticyclone%20grips%20northern%20Italy%20and%20the%20Po%20Valley%2C%20pushing%20temperatures%20well%20above%20the%20seasonal%20average.%3Cp%3ESimone%20Padovani%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETourists%20on%20the%20Ponte%20della%20Paglia%20bridge%20in%20Venice%20carried%20umbrellas%20for%20some%20relief%20from%20the%20sun.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223713%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tourists%20in%20the%20sun%20in%20Venice.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d49cb360acd489560b43a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222475%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVENICE%2C%20ITALY%20-%20JUNE%2024%3A%20Tourists%20in%20the%20sun%20on%20the%20Ponte%20della%20Paglia%2C%20opposite%20the%20Bridge%20of%20Sighs%2C%20at%20the%20height%20of%20a%20severe%20heatwave%2C%20on%20June%2024%2C%202026%20in%20Venice%2C%20Italy.%20Venice%20is%20gripped%20by%20a%20severe%20heatwave%2C%2034%C2%B0C%20at%2012%3A30%2C%20with%20highs%20of%20up%20to%2038%C2%B0C%20forecast%20across%20the%20Po%20Valley%20this%20weekend%2C%20and%20its%20very%20fabric%20makes%20it%20a%20hotspot%3A%20stone%20and%20masonry%2C%20narrow%20alleys%20that%20trap%20heat%2C%20almost%20no%20greenery%2C%20and%20lagoon%20humidity%20that%20deepens%20the%20mugginess%20and%20blocks%20night-time%20cooling.%20The%20cost%20falls%20above%20all%20on%20an%20ageing%2C%20shrinking%20resident%20population%2C%20now%20below%2048%2C000%20in%20the%20historic%20centre.%20The%20city%20is%20ill-equipped%3A%20no%20network%20of%20climate%20shelters%2C%20few%20drinking%20fountains%2C%20poorly%20distributed%20and%20absent%20from%20crowded%20hubs%20such%20as%20St%20Mark's%20and%20Rialto%2C%20and%20little%20relief%20beyond%20stepping%20into%20bars%2C%20museums%20or%20churches%3B%20air%20conditioning%20is%20limited%20and%20contentious%2C%20between%20heritage%20limits%20on%20external%20units%20and%20the%20heat%20they%20would%20pour%20into%20the%20alleys.%20This%20fragility%20is%20set%20against%20better-equipped%20Po%20Valley%20cities%20such%20as%20Bologna%2C%20with%20its%20network%20of%20climate%20shelters.%20Venice%20features%20in%20Padus%20as%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20urban%20face%20of%20the%20eastern%20Po%20Valley%2C%20where%20the%20Po%20system%20meets%20the%20sea%20and%20the%20same%20heat-and-water%20crisis%20striking%20the%20farmland%20also%20hits%20the%20cities.%20Italy's%20Po%20Valley%2C%20shaped%20by%20the%20river%20Po%20-%20known%20as%20Padus%20in%20ancient%20times%2C%20is%20one%20of%20Europe's%20most%20intensively%20cultivated%20and%20densely%20populated%20regions.%20It%20is%20characterised%20by%20extensive%20irrigation%20networks%2C%20high%20concentrations%20of%20livestock%20farming%20and%20major%20food%20distribution%20systems.%20It%20is%20al