ut%20deal%20is%20on%20the%20Trtl%20Travel%20Pillow%2C%20a%20godsend%20for%20upright%2C%20middle%2C%20and%20aisle-seaters%2C%20or%20anyone%20seeking%20extra%20neck%20support.%20For%20Prime%20Day%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126731259af-20%26h%3D55cc2346ae76f1479302a4eb0d5ef39fdd49eb05c3cc9409fd9eaa56bf9468ce%26postID%3D6a3d5a63778476c08ad0bfaa%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fdeals%252Ftrtl-travel-pillow-prime-day-deal-2026-6%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FTrtl-Pillow-Scientifically-Support-Washable%252Fdp%252FB00LB7REBE%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit's%20%2439.70%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%2038%25%20off%20and%20its%20lowest%20price%20since%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20this%20pillow%20back%20in%20April%20so%20I'd%20have%20it%20for%20my%208-hour%20flights%20to%20and%20from%20Italy.%20I'd%20seen%20the%20Trtl%20Pillow%20on%20many%20best-of%20lists%20but%20was%20always%20skeptical.%20Rather%20than%20a%20plush%20or%20inflatable%20pillow%2C%20it's%20an%20ergonomic%20design%20incorporating%20a%20piece%20of%20molded%20plastic%20wrapped%20in%20lightweight%20fleece.%20You%20position%20the%20plastic%20along%20one%20side%20of%20your%20neck%2C%20then%20wrap%20the%20fleece%20around%20to%20achieve%20a%20secure%20fit%20with%20your%20neck%20in%20a%20neutral%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Italy%20and%20a%20recent%20road%20trip%20where%20I%20took%20some%20hourslong%20naps%2C%20I'm%20happy%20to%20report%20that%20I%20won't%20leave%20home%20without%20this%20pillow%20in%20the%20future%20%E2%80%94%20my%20neck%20pain%20didn't%20creep%20up%20on%20me.%20Insider%20Reviews%20editor%20Gabi%20Chase%20feels%20the%20same.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20only%20travel%20pillow%20I've%20tried%20that%20fits%20my%20long%2C%20thin%20neck%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20wrap%20is%20easily%20adjustable%20and%20kept%20my%20head%20in%20a%20fixed%20position%2C%20sparing%20me%20from%20the%20agonizing%20cycle%20of%20headbobbing%20and%20shocking%20myself%20awake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2280217bd8-1439-485d-9894-5a3470563aec%5C%22%3EWhy%20we%20love%20the%20Trtl%20Travel%20Pillow%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20fleece%20scarf%20and%20with%20trtl%20logo%20is%20shown%20with%20a%20plastic%20neck%20support%20insert%20beside%20a%20trtl%20pouch%20with%20clip.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d74c8e218c3b62535d3bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Trtl%20Travel%20Pillow%20consists%20of%20a%20lightweight%20fleece%20scarf%20and%20plastic%20neck%20support%2C%20and%20it%20can%20be%20carried%20in%20a%20convenient%20pouch.%3Cp%3ELisa%20Sabatini%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnmatched%20ergonomic%20support%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUpright%20sleepers%20won't%20find%20the%20same%20level%20of%20support%20in%20other%20travel%20pillows.%20Some%20standard%20plush%20or%20inflatable%20pillows%20are%20designed%20for%20upright%20sleep%2C%20but%20none%20offer%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20Trtl.%20This%20is%20key%20for%20people%20with%20long%2C%20thin%20necks%20or%20chronic%20neck%20pain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELow%20profile%20means%20less%20bulk%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20you%20dislike%20the%20standard%2C%20bulky%20U-ring%20pillows%20like%20I%20do%2C%20the%20Trtl%20Pillow%20has%20an%20incredibly%20thin%20profile%20and%20weighs%20just%204.6%20ounces.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20pillow%20fits%20neatly%20inside%20its%20convenient%20carry%20pouch%2C%20which%20features%20a%20carabiner%20for%20clipping%20to%20your%20luggage%20or%20backpack.%20Combined%2C%20the%20pillow%20and%20pouch%20weigh%20a%20mere%206.3%20ounces.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEasy%20to%20clean%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20have%20