t%20to%20get%20off%20my%20phone%20and%20deal%20with%20burnout%2C%20I%20found%20the%20perfect%20low-pressure%20social%20activity%20to%20do%20after%20work%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20smiling%20holding%20copy%20of%20the%20handmaid's%20tale%20book%20and%20a%20coffee%20mug%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3444aa0e60dfb3f373f46e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20realized%20that%20attending%20reading%20parties%20is%20the%20perfect%20low-pressure%20social%20activity%20for%20me%20after%20a%20long%20day%20of%20working.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Mautner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMost%20days%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20feeling%20exhausted%2C%20burned%20out%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforced-myself-say-yes-all-plans-off-phone-made-friends-2026-3%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eglued%20to%20my%20phone%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESo%2C%20I%20began%20attending%20reading%20parties%2C%20laid-back%20hangs%20where%20people%20gather%20to%20read%20independently.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20the%20perfect%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhost-monthly-party-changed-my-social-life-2025-1%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elow-pressure%20social%20activity%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20me%20to%20feel%20refreshed%20and%20get%20off%20my%20phone.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20work%20each%20day%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20feeling%20mentally%20exhausted%20and%20burned%20out.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeemingly%20endless%20emails%20and%20a%20phone%20that%20buzzes%20long%20after%205%20p.m.%20left%20me%20craving%20a%20more%20balanced%20lifestyle%2C%20particularly%20one%20that%20didn't%20make%20me%20feel%20constantly%20available.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20was%20struggling%20to%20find%20activities%20and%20plans%20that%20would%20actually%20stick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fdoes-exercise-make-you-happy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexercise%20can%20be%20mood-boosting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I%20tried%20going%20to%20the%20gym%20after%20work.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20though%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20canceling%20because%20I%20was%20too%20tired%20and%20it%20didn't%20sound%20like%20much%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20attempted%20to%20make%20regular%20plans%20to%20go%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foffice-quiet-but-happy-hour-still-kicking-after-pandemic-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehappy%20hour%20with%20coworkers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20didn't%20stick%2C%20either%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20exactly%20want%20all%20my%20social%20interactions%20to%20revolve%20around%20alcohol.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20continued%20spending%20most%20evenings%20sitting%20on%20my%20couch%2C%20doomscrolling%20on%20Instagram%2C%20waiting%20for%20my%20husband%20to%20get%20home%20from%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20after%20checking%20my%20screen-time%20settings%2C%20I%20was%20horrified%20to%20realize%20I%20was%20spending%20an%20average%20of%20four%20hours%20a%20day%20on%20my%20phone.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20told%20my%20friend%20about%20my%20unsuccessful%20attempts%20to%20fix%20my%20post-work%20habits%2C%20she%20suggested%20I%20attend%20a%20reading%20party%20(or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsilentbook.club%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESilent%20Book%20Club%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20seen%20people%20around%20the%20world%20posting%20about%20attending%20these%20low-pressure%20events%2C%20where%20attendees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarting-neighborhood-book-club-to-make-real-friends-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egather%20to%20read%20books%3C%2Fa%3E%20independently%20and%20silently%2C%20then%20have%20discussions%20afterward.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seemed%20strange%20to%20turn%20an%20activity%20I%20usually%20do%20alone%20into%20a%20group%20one%2C%20but%20I%20was%20willing%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246365def-f729-4bae-920d-115b1bbb74d2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20skeptical%2C%20but%20the%20reading%20party%20helped%20me%20get%20off%20my%20phone%20in%20a%20fun%20way%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20table%20with%20coffee%20cups%2C%20books%20in%20cafe%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3441d8f4bed3c6152cbc7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221086%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reading%20party%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20perfect%20low-pressure%20activity.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Mautner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20I%20headed%20to%20a%20reading%20party%20at%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20near%20me%20with%20a%20copy%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-handmaids-tale-about-hulu-2017-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Handmaid's%20Tale%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20hand.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20arrived%2C%20I%20was%20worried%20I'd%20be%20the%20only%20one%20in%20attendance.%20Instead%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20about%20a%20dozen%20people%20spread%20out%20at%20tables%20in%20the%20back%20corner%20of%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20%E2%80%94%20all%20with%20books%20in%20hand%2C%20coffees%20nearby%2C%20and%20no%20phones%20in%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20smiled%20at%20me%20and%20scooted%20over%2C%20so%20I%20could%20sit%20at%20the%20empty%20seat%20beside%20her.%20I%20pulled%20out%20my%20book%2C%20ordered%20an%20oat-milk%20latte%2C%20and%20tried%20to%20start%20reading.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20kept%20getting%20distracted%20and%20couldn't%20get%20comfortable%20in%20the%20chair.%20I%20shifted%20from%20side%20to%20side%20and%20had%20to%20reread%20the%20same%20page%20three%20times%20because%20I%20kept%20looking%20up%20at%20the%20sound%20of%20the%20espresso%20machine%20or%20someone%20walking%20by.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wondered%20how%20long%20I%20could%20possibly%20sit%20here%20like%20this%20as%20I%20resisted%20the%20urge%20to%20grab%20my%20phone%20to%20check%20the%20time.%20Everyone%20else's%20were%20away%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20judged%20for%20having%20mine%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%2020%20minutes%2C%20I%20finally%20got%20comfortable%20and%20was%20able%20to%20really%20dive%20into%20my%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20group%20read%2C%20uninterrupted%2C%20for%20one%20and%20a%20half%20hours%2C%20and%20then%20the%20woman%20who%20had%20organized%20the%20event%20got%20our%20attention%20and%20said%20the%20reading%20part%20of%20the%20event%20was%20finished.%20She%20motioned%20for%20us%20to%20go%20around%20in%20a%20circle%2C%20introduce%20ourselves%2C%20and%20share%20what%20we%20were%20reading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20everyone%20was%20through%2C%20attendees%20chatted%20with%20the%20people%20beside%20them.%20The%20conversations%20flowed%20naturally.%20We%20all%20liked%20reading%20and%20set%20aside%20time%20in%20our%20schedules%20to%20go%20there%2C%20so%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20break%20the%20ice.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20out%20the%20girl%20next%20to%20me%20was%20also%20a%20big%20Bukowski%20fan%2C%20and%20it%20was%20nice%20to%20pick%20each%20other's%20brains%20about%20our%20favorite%20works%20of%20his.%20Shortly%20after%2C%20the%20event%20came%20to%20a%20close.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20began%20to%20leave%2C%20and%20I%20liked%20not%20feeling%20pressured%20to%20exchange%20Instagram%20handles%20or%20phone%20numbers%20with%20anyone.%20I%20simply%20thanked%20the%20host%20and%20said%20I'd%20be%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20feeling%20refreshed%20and%20calm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ffd3bc9-5ea3-468c-9f5c-3ff8e6063ae6%5C%22%3EIt's%20nice%20having%20semi-regular%20plans%20that%20help%20me%20connect%20with%20others%20in%20a%20low-pressure%20way%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227952%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20view%20of%20people%20in%20coffee%20shop%20reading%20books%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3440630e60dfb3f373f3cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUltimately%2C%20I%20enjoy%20the%20calmness%20and%20productivity%20of%20the%20reading%20parties.%3Cp%3EFG%20Trade%20Latin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20looking%20down%20at%20my%20phone%20during%20my%20walk%20home%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20enjoying%20the%20beauty%20of%20my%20neighborhood%20%E2%80%94%20people%20walking%20their%20dogs%2C%20chatting%20in%20caf%C3%A9s.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20continued%2C%20a%20buzz%20in%20my%20bag%20snapped%20me%20out%20of%20the%20present%20moment.%20Without%20thinking%2C%20my%20hand%20shot%20into%20my%20purse%20and%20grabbed%20it.%20I%20laughed%20when%20I%20saw%20that%20I%20had%20no%20important%20messages%2C%20only%20a%20promotional%20email%20about%20a%20sale%20at%20Ikea.%20I%20had%20missed%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20won't%20say%20this%20event%20was%20a%20magic%20cure%20that's%20made%20me%20never%20reach%20for%20my%20phone%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-deal-with-anxiety-at-work-2016-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efeel%20stressed%20after%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20it%20helped%20me%20to%20connect%20with%20others%20and%20myself%20in%20a%20more%20present%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20now%20been%20attending%20these%20parties%20every%20other%20week%20or%20so%20for%20about%20six%20months.%20It's%20gotten%20easier%20to%20get%20comfortable%2C%20stay%20focused%20on%20the%20page%20I'm%20reading%2C%20make%20post-reading%20conversation%2C%20and%20not%20feel%20tempted%20to%20grab%20my%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20I'm%20truly%20desperate%20to%20know%20what%20time%20it%20is%2C%20I%20just%20look%20at%20the%20watch%20that%20I'd%20forgotten%20I%20owned.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffound-perfect-low-pressure-social-activity-after-work-reading-parties-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782413282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a344dd00e60dfb3f373f53a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffound-perfect-low-pressure-social-activity-after-work-reading-parties-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Attending%20reading%20parties%20and%20Silent%20Book%20Clubs%20helped%20me%20get%20off%20my%20phone%2C%20socialize%20in%20a%20low-pressure%20way%2C%20and%20deal%20with%20burnout%20after%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Mautner)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UN%20suspends%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20evacuation%20after%20ship%20'hit%20by%20projectile'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782413220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F26%2F06%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-oman-strait-of-hormuz_7277509.jpg%3F20260619093024%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fun-suspends-strait-of-hormuz-evacuation-after-ship-hit-by-projectile-13557819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UN%20has%20halted%20the%20evacuation%20of%20thousands%20of%20seafarers%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20after%20a%20vessel%20came%20under%20a%20suspected%20attack.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fun-suspends-strait-of-hormuz-evacuation-after-ship-hit-by-projectile-13557819%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Want%20to%20die%20as%20an%20Indian%3A%2094-year-old%20Andhra%20woman%20renounces%20US%20citizenship%2C%20meets%20collect