t%20another%20round%20of%20Xbox%20price%20hikes%20hours%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-price-increases-mac-ipad-memory-chip-tim-cook-iphone-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%20boosted%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaken%20together%2C%20the%20price%20increases%20%E2%80%94%20which%20both%20companies%20say%20are%20due%20to%20spiking%20memory%20and%20storage%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20are%20set%20to%20make%20holiday%20shopping%20significantly%20more%20expensive.%20For%20gamers%2C%20it%20makes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprice-gaming-inflation-xbox-playstation-nintendo-switch-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egaming%20increasingly%20feel%20like%20a%20luxury%20hobby%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20popular%20Xbox%20game%20consoles%20are%20set%20to%20increase%20by%20%24100-%24150%20on%20August%201.%20The%20512%20GB%20models%20will%20go%20up%20by%20%24100%2C%20and%20the%201%20TB%20versions%20will%20increase%20by%20%24150.%20The%20Xbox%20with%20the%20highest%20available%20storage%20configuration%20of%202%20TB%20will%20be%20discontinued%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLast%20October%2C%20we%20increased%20XBOX%20console%20price%20by%20%2420-%2470%20in%20the%20U.S.%20We%20hoped%20another%20price%20increase%20would%20not%20be%20necessary%2C%20and%20we%20have%20spent%20the%20last%20several%20months%20working%20with%20suppliers%20on%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20said%20in%20a%20blog%20post.%20%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20console%20storage%20and%20memory%20prices%20have%20increased%20by%20more%20than%202.5x%20and%20we%20expect%20another%20doubling%20by%20the%20fall%20of%202027.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20price%20hikes%20will%20apply%20worldwide.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20third%20time%20Microsoft%20has%20raised%20prices%20on%20its%20latest%20Xbox%20generation%2C%20following%20increases%20in%20May%20and%20October%202025.%20The%20Xbox%20Series%20X%20is%20now%20%24250%20to%20%24300%20more%20expensive%20than%20it%20was%20when%20it%20launched%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memory%20shortage%20has%20impacted%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20consumer%20electronics%20companies%2C%20many%20of%20which%20have%20raised%20prices%20in%20the%20last%208%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20chief%20rivals%20in%20the%20gaming%20wars%2C%20PlayStation%20and%20Nintendo%2C%20have%20both%20previously%20announced%20price%20increases%20for%20the%20PS5%20and%20Nintendo%20Switch%202%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComputers%2C%20which%20also%20rely%20on%20memory%20and%20storage%20chips%2C%20have%20also%20become%20more%20costly%20to%20produce%2C%20and%20Apple%20followed%20many%20of%20its%20peers%20in%20boosting%20MacBook%20and%20iMac%20prices%2C%20along%20with%20the%20iPad%2C%20Apple%20TV%2C%20HomePod%2C%20and%20Vision%20Pro%2C%20on%20Thursday%20%E2%80%94%20by%20as%20much%20as%20%24300.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20consumer%20electronics%20industry%20is%20struggling%20with%20the%20current%20components%20crisis%2C%20but%20the%20effects%20are%20particularly%20hard%20on%20consoles%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20said.%20%26quot%3BUnlike%20phones%2C%20computers%2C%20speakers%2C%20and%20other%20consumer%20devices%2C%20consoles%20are%20typically%20not%20sold%20at%20a%20profit%2C%20but%20instead%20for%20less%20than%20they%20cost%20to%20make.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20blog%20post%20announcing%20the%20coming%20price%20hikes%2C%20Microsoft%20shared%20details%20on%20programs%20it%20said%20%26quot%3Bmake%20XBOX%20consoles%20more%20accessible%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20buy-now-pay-later%20and%20interest-free%20financing%20services%2C%20along%20with%20efforts%20to%20make%20previously%20used%20game%20consoles%20available%20via%20retailers%20to%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-xbox-price-increase-series-x-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusi