ers.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFord%20says%20AI%20and%20automation%20helped%20its%20quality%20turnaround%2C%20but%20they%20were%20not%20enough%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExecs%20told%20reporters%20they%20hired%20or%20brought%20back%20350%20technical%20specialists%20to%20catch%20defects%20earlier.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20overhaul%20helped%20Ford%20top%20JD%20Power%20after%20years%20of%20quality%20problems%20and%20expensive%20recalls.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fford%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFord%3C%2Fa%3E%20staged%20a%20quality%20comeback.%20The%20automaker%20credits%20part%20of%20the%20turnaround%20to%20pairing%20AI%20with%20something%20more%20old-school%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-mechanics-free-carhartt-auto-tech-scholars-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eveteran%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecutives%20at%20Ford%20told%20reporters%20this%20week%20that%20the%20company%20had%20hired%2C%20promoted%2C%20or%20brought%20back%20about%20350%20experienced%20technical%20specialists%20as%20part%20of%20a%20sweeping%20effort%20to%20fix%20vehicle-quality%20problems.%20Those%20engineering%20veterans%20have%20helped%20mentor%20younger%20staff%2C%20lead%20design%20reviews%2C%20and%20improve%20the%20AI%20and%20automated%20quality%20tools%20Ford%20uses%20to%20catch%20defects%20before%20vehicles%20reach%20customers%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20offered%20a%20striking%20admission%3A%20AI%20and%20automation%20were%20not%20enough%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArtificial%20intelligence%20is%20a%20fantastic%20tool%2C%20but%20it's%20only%20as%20good%20as%20information%20you%20use%20to%20train%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Charles%20Poon%2C%20Ford's%20vice%20president%20of%20vehicle%20hardware%20engineering%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BMistakenly%2C%20we%20thought%20that%20by%20just%20introducing%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20ingesting%20the%20design%20requirements%20that%20we%20had%2C%20that%20would%20produce%20a%20high-quality%20product.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoon%20said%20Ford%20had%20not%20done%20enough%20in%20prior%20years%20to%20preserve%20the%20knowledge%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-ceo-jim-farley-worker-shortage-manufacturing-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emost%20experienced%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20left%20the%20company%20before%20their%20expertise%20was%20fully%20integrated%20into%20Ford's%20systems.%20He%20said%20quality%20problems%20often%20showed%20up%20at%20the%20boundaries%20between%20teams%2C%20where%20design%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20software%2C%20and%20hardware%20collide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c620e6b1-0761-4739-a7ee-77538a5a0d9e%5C%22%3EQuality%20win%2C%20recall%20hangover%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Ford%20assembly%20worker%20uses%20a%20hose-like%20instrument%20on%20the%20Ford%20F-150%20factory%20line.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d4b9de218c3b62535d0ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFord%20just%20improved%20its%20standing%20in%20one%20of%20the%20auto%20industry's%20biggest%20yearly%20tests.%3Cp%3EBill%20Pugliano%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20came%20as%20Ford%20celebrated%20a%20major%20milestone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumer%20data%20analytics%20firm%20JD%20Power%20named%20Ford%20the%20top%20mass-market%20brand%20in%20its%20latest%20initial-quality%20study%2C%20trailing%20only%20Porsche%20and%20Genesis%20overall%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study%20released%20Thursday.%20Ford%20narrowly%20beat%20Lexus%2C%20which%20has%20long%20been%20one%20of%20the%20strongest%20performers%20in%20the%20rankings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20big%20turnaround.%20Just%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20Ford%20ranked%2015th%20out%20of%2025%20major%20automakers%20in%20the%20same%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20Ford%20has%20faced%20headwinds%20on%20its%20product%20quality.%20In%202025%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-recalls-police-cars-explorer-suv-mustang-f-150-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFord%20issued%20152%20recalls%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20nearly%20doubling%20the%20previous%20record%20set%20by%20General%20Motors%20in%202014%20with%2077%20safety%20bulletins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Thursday%2C%20Ford%20had%20issued%2051%20recalls%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20NHTSA's%20dashboard.%20That's%20still%20more%20than%20double%20Chrysler%2C%20the%20next-closest%20automaker%2C%20which%20had%20issued%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFord%20executives%20said%20many%20of%20the%20continued%20recall%20issues%20are%20tied%20to%20vehicles%20and%20platforms%20designed%20between%202013%20and%202020%2C%20calling%20recalls%20a%20%26quot%3Blagging%20indicator.%26quot%3B%20They%20framed%20the%20JD%20Power%20win%20as%20proof%20that%20a%20new%20approach%20is%20taking%20hold%2C%20and%20said%20internal%20data%20shows%20%26quot%3Bclear%20improvement%26quot%3B%20in%20newer%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20initial-quality%20study%20measures%20problems%20in%20new%20vehicles%2C%20not%20long-term%20durability%2C%20making%20it%20an%20early%20signal%20rather%20than%20a%20full%20verdict%20on%20whether%20Ford%20has%20solved%20its%20recall%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2d29269-b137-4241-82af-fb385a94afb7%5C%22%3EFord%20says%20it%20changed%20how%20it%20catches%20problems%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blue%20Ford%20Explorer%20SUV%20is%20parked%20on%20a%20dealership%20lot.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d4d6fa25092c74cc9f31e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFord%20says%20it's%20been%20making%20manufacturing%20quality%20improvements%20since%202023.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFord%20launched%20its%20quality%20reset%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20time%2C%20Kumar%20Galhotra%2C%20Ford's%20COO%2C%20said%20the%20company%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20its%20technical%20specialist%20population.%20Those%20specialists%20now%20lead%20mandatory%20design%20reviews%20and%20look%20for%20failure%20points%20before%20parts%20ever%20reach%20the%20plant%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20hunt%20for%20failure%20points%20before%20a%20part%20ever%20reaches%20the%20plant%20floor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20created%20an%20industrial%20system%20team%20to%20bring%20engineering%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20supply%20chain%20closer%20together.%20Before%20that%20approach%2C%20Galhotra%20said%20Ford%20had%20previously%20relied%20too%20heavily%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bfind%20and%20fix%26quot%3B%20approach%20%E2%80%94%20identifying%20problems%20after%20they%20appeared%20and%20trying%20to%20resolve%20them%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Ford%20says%20it%20is%20trying%20to%20prevent%20problems%20before%20they%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFord%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20had%20developed%20two%20bespoke%20AI-enhanced%20scanning%20tools%20that%20helped%20validate%20that%20cars%20were%20properly%20assembled%20before%20rolling%20off%20the%20lot.%20The%20tools%2C%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-uses-ai-cameras-in-factories-prevent-recalls-costly-rework-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAiTriz%20and%20MAIVs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20both%20debuted%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ford%20has%20previously%20said%20the%20tools%20are%20helping%20improve%20product%20quality%2C%20the%20company%20did%20not%20say%20whether%20the%20350%20specialists%20worked%20directly%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-ai-hiring-veteran-engineers-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782408018000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d2fcbe218c3b62535cf34%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-ai-hiring-veteran-engineers-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ford%20won%20a%20major%20quality%20award%20after%20years%20of%20recall%20headaches.%20It%20says%20the%20turnaround%20came%20from%20veteran%20engineers%20and%20rethinking%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bshimkus%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Shimkus)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A94%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Non-citizens%20arriving%20at%20US%20border%20do%20not%20automatically%20get%20asylum%2C%20can%20be%20turned%20away%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782407267000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131998820%2Cimgsize-395338.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnon-citizens-arriving-at-us-border-do-not-automatically-get-asylum-can-be-turned-away-supreme-court-backs-trump-administration%2Farticleshow%2F131998673.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131998673.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A95%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnon-citizens-arriving-at-us-border-do-not-automatically-get-asylum-can-be-turned-away-supreme-court-backs-trump-administration%2Farticleshow%2F131998673.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnon-citizens-arriving-at-us-border-do-not-automatical