%20to%20his%20work%20in%20putting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F190973%2Findia-first-wildlife-underpass-kanha-pench-corridor-tigers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20corridors%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20when%20India%E2%80%99s%20Supreme%20Court%20earmarked%20the%20Sigur%20Plateau%20%E2%80%94%20which%20sees%20the%20movement%20of%20around%206%2C300%20Asiatic%20Elephants%20%E2%80%94%20as%20an%20elephant%20corridor%2C%20%3Cem%3EWhitley%20Fund%20for%20Nature%3C%2Fem%3E%20notes%20how%20the%20apex%20court%20used%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20evidence%20of%20the%20benefits%20to%20both%20wildlife%20and%20people.%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20created%20ripples%3B%20shaping%20the%20crux%20of%20wildlife%20policies%20as%20we%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20can%20sit%20and%20listen%20to%20him%20for%20hours.%20But%20I%20know%20he%20has%20somewhere%20to%20be%3B%20I%E2%80%99m%20keeping%20a%20hundred%20and%20fifty%20of%20his%20jungle%20friends%20waiting%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20one%20last%20question%20before%20you%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20say%2C%20unable%20to%20stop%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20do%20you%20see%20in%20them%20that%20connects%20you%20to%20them%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20near%20persons%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20them%20in%20terms%20of%20conscience%2C%20memory%2C%20and%20intellect.%20They%20are%20very%20similar%20to%20us.%20They%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20understand%20my%20words%20or%20my%20language.%20But%20they%20understand%20me%20in%20other%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20before%20he%20concludes%20our%20conversation%20to%20head%20to%20the%20place%20where%20he%20feels%20most%20at%20home%20%E2%80%94%20amid%20the%20elephants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Ce